  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Prescription of medicines by telephone in French medical call Centres is a part of the
      general practitioners activity.

      This study aimed to described drug prescription by phone (MTP) performed in four medical call
      centers. The primary objective is to evaluate adherence to french practice guidelines for the
      drug prescription by phone (Haute Autorité de Santé, 2009) The secondary objective is to
      evaluate the risk/benefit ratio for drug prescription by phone.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
